Complete the function that takes a sequence of numbers as single parameter. Your function must return the sum of the even
values of this sequence.Only numbers without decimals like 4 or 4.0 can be even.
The input is a sequence of numbers: integers and/or floats.

https://www.codewars.com/kata/586beb5ba44cfc44ed0006c3

function sumEvenNumbers(input) {
let arr = [];
  let sum = 0;
  for ( let i = 0; i < input.length; i++){
    if ( input[i] % 2 === 0)
      sum = sum + input[i];
  }
  return sum;
}
